      id="mongoc_gridfs_file_set_metadata">
  <info>
    <link type="guide" xref="mongoc_gridfs_file_t" group="function"/>
  </info>
  <title>mongoc_gridfs_file_set_metadata()</title>

  <section id="synopsis">
    <title>Synopsis</title>
    <synopsis><code mime="text/x-csrc"><![CDATA[void
mongoc_gridfs_file_set_metadata (mongoc_gridfs_file_t *file,
                                 const bson_t         *metadata);]]></code></synopsis>
  </section>

  <section id="parameters">
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <table>
      <tr><td><p>file</p></td><td><p>A <code xref="mongoc_gridfs_file_t">mongoc_gridfs_file_t</code>.</p></td></tr>
      <tr><td><p>bson</p></td><td><p>A <code xref="bson:bson_t">bson_t</code> containing metadata for <code>file</code>.</p></td></tr>
    </table>
  </section>

  <section id="description">
    <title>Description</title>
    <p>Sets the metadata associated with <code>file</code>.</p>
    <p>You need to call <code xref="mongoc_gridfs_file_save">mongoc_gridfs_file_save()</code> to persist this change.</p>
  </section>

